&lt;p&gt;Increasingly complex businesses are building integrations on top of the Claude Developer Platform. The Platform Tools team has a goal to spend time with these customers, learn what they need in order to build the integrations they need to build, and improve the platform to support these use cases.&lt;/p&gt;
